Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.83,0:01:50.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王…所要找的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.55,0:02:12.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫雷国，好久没来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.06,0:02:15.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久…也只不过是三年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是城里的样子真的改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:21.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人增加了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为战争的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有许多难民跑过来这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想要得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.74,0:02:32.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是能够这样和平的生活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许只有夫雷国和莱登而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有人打架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.82,0:02:44.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是   去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.92,0:02:47.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是帕母我们要早点到卡修王 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.93,0:02:53.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.37,0:03:01.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧，亲爱的     爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.84,0:03:07.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不感谢卡修王让你们留下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然还敢偷东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.05,0:03:11.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是可恶的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在卡修王这个国家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:19.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷东西是属於重罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.17,0:03:30.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要讲的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.11,0:03:46.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然对那种没武器的人动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.48,0:03:49.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个小偷，他偷了小麦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.26,0:03:54.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就把他驱逐出境就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修殿下他是不会这样做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.33,0:04:00.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴，没关系的人别插手管闲事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来，这样只会让自己受伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，我会控制力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有哪个不怕被打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.92,0:04:27.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们这些人救了盗匪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.93,0:04:37.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还把士兵打伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.97,0:04:40.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，你也要听我解释
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.30,0:04:43.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴，如果你投降的话就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.94,0:04:46.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话就当场立即斩首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.34,0:04:49.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来用讲的也没有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，不可以，你不可以和他们打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.45,0:04:55.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…等等，大家把剑放下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.89,0:05:03.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你就是帕母大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.69,0:05:05.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了这夫雷国的帕母大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是叫帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你讲我救夫雷国就太言过其实了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.77,0:05:14.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很失礼，想不到你会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.57,0:05:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也有错，不应该这么明目张胆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为看到士兵对那些难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.41,0:05:24.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常无礼，所以才插手管的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.88,0:05:26.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样我也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近年来了不少的难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使这里的粮食发生了短缺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.66,0:05:35.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是难民还是一直进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:39.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对!还有因为市民对难民的排斥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以这种事是常有的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母大人是有事而来的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那请让我们带你到城堡里去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过他和卡修王交情不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.88,0:05:56.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知道他原来那么出名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我看中的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:01.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以应该不会差到哪里去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:05.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.03,0:06:12.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救了夫雷国的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你们在这间房间内稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  谢谢你带路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.21,0:06:32.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是夫雷的少年骑士队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.18,0:06:36.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就是在训练将来的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出胜负了  史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.33,0:06:49.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…还没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的潜质不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且眼睛很有神  那个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.87,0:06:57.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是以前的你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.64,0:06:59.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.13,0:07:18.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讲过你们不用行礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把你们当成是朋友看待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见  卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是卡修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的佣兵王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.97,0:07:31.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神很不错啊，帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有三个人是新面孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中二个应该是士兵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.98,0:07:40.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又发生什么事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们是有事想来拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.95,0:07:46.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，原来是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是太凑巧J
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思，卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:57.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们也是为了要消灭煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正准备出兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是住在那火龙山的红龙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对!那魔龙煞星现在正是觅食期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的范围已经到夫雷国的西边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.02,0:08:18.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在夫雷的西边有遍绿色的平原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是魔龙煞星觅食之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有人敢去动它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在有许多难民进入夫雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.17,0:08:32.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有最重要的粮食问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.10,0:08:35.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我为了要解决难民和粮食问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.51,0:08:40.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然知道危险也在那里盖起房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.01,0:08:41.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为受到煞星的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:51.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说村子里没有一个生还者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是残忍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.33,0:08:58.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是我想得太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是为了解决问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常需要那块土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:05.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲得对，沙漠的夫雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.60,0:09:08.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确是需要那种平原
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我对那毁掉村子的煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都不可以原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.08,0:09:17.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们正准备出战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.71,0:09:20.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样，我们当然尽全力帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.02,0:09:25.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是帕母，圣龙岛那边怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.26,0:09:26.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的水龙和煞星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.83,0:09:35.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们根本不知道是在谁手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果那王锡是在水龙身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们去把那煞星打败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉就趁机去打水龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.51,0:09:46.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他拿到王锡之後就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很简单，火龙的平原和圣龙岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二边都去就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.22,0:09:58.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要把军队分成二队的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那战斗力就减弱了许多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.19,0:10:05.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也要顾到夫雷国的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.36,0:10:06.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用那么多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚喜拉他也没有带着军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.20,0:10:12.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们也以少数出战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重质不重量  对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.27,0:10:21.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重质不重量  讲得真轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这却是个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.85,0:10:27.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以陛下，水龙就交给我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要对付煞星本来就不预我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.89,0:10:37.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们就应该去对付另一只
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，你和蒂都留下帮忙陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.70,0:10:44.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争一定要用到魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.00,0:10:47.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且要去圣龙岛的领队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想请波里森做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.57,0:10:51.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要波里森做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.41,0:11:00.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏的颜色好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听讲魔龙煞星已经开始出来行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.56,0:11:13.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我们所要对付的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.67,0:11:18.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了，欧布…怕了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.57,0:11:22.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，战争之神会保护我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不会辜负我对你的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.84,0:11:56.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要波里森做领队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.17,0:12:00.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，在途中我一直在想着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能让你脱离愤怒精灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎样才能让你不变成狂战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果答案就在面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.92,0:12:12.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是帕母   你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…  因为你经过多次旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.16,0:12:17.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了不少的经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.73,0:12:20.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为领队的你，比我们任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.53,0:12:24.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定拥有更多的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，让他感受更多的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後从愤怒精灵中排除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他因为没感情所以很冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当领队时要做决定也是有帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是欠缺冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，我并不是做领队的料子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果在战争中又变成狂战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能保证不会伤害你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.73,0:12:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是期待着你的坚强的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有那领队般的想法行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.14,0:13:03.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後会发生什么事你心里都明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.77,0:13:07.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来你一定可以恢复过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错，试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果成功就可以不用再变狂战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.69,0:13:22.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.83,0:13:24.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希利斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何，好看吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去借衣服来参加这个舞会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.74,0:13:40.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，一起跳舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不… 我不大会跳舞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，不会也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.51,0:13:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.35,0:13:52.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该是帕母的女朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.99,0:13:59.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是人类我是贺而夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.27,0:14:06.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是希利斯好像很中意帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.44,0:14:09.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波里森  你对她有什么感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.11,0:14:10.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我没有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没尝试过爱情的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.81,0:14:18.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，但是没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的旅行一定能帮到你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.62,0:14:22.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.22,0:14:25.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然叫我做领队就没意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.32,0:14:28.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，跟我这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.09,0:14:33.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛长到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.23,0:14:36.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡修王… 非常的抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.13,0:14:40.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，你叫希利斯吧，真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.37,0:14:46.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何，玩得很高兴吗  帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.18,0:14:47.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 ... 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真诚实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是想要让他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去对付龙的信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.65,0:14:55.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想让他们去之前放松心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做不对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.82,0:15:01.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是让他们陷入痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.26,0:15:03.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是国王的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.86,0:15:05.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们从痛苦中爬出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是国王的职责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讲得对，在还没打败煞星时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不算是救了夫雷和那些难民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.14,0:15:16.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有亚喜拉的野心也别忘记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.11,0:15:17.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 ...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母，介绍给你认识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是中午的那个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫史派克，很精灵的一个小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.82,0:15:30.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在城堡里一边做事  一边学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.62,0:15:34.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫史派克，能见到你真高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我梦想是成为一个像你一样的骑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.46,0:15:43.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只史派克，这夫雷国里的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.17,0:15:47.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都拿你做榜样  帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么讲我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你史派克，你一定可以成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.61,0:15:55.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做个比我更棒的骑士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母和我跳舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.55,0:16:03.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了，帕母，好久没有比赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.12,0:16:05.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先邀请帕母的人是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么，虽然你没有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.17,0:16:23.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你也要奉承一下讲我漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.92,0:16:39.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认输了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害，不愧是卡修殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.28,0:17:02.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办，我要怎么做...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.81,0:17:05.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了．就这样结束了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.12,0:17:14.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我服输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一击没有对准重要部位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.59,0:17:19.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你还有点犹豫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你认为这剑不赢就会死的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.66,0:17:25.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你会打赢我也讲不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:26.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.84,0:17:30.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.41,0:17:34.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想做王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.25,0:17:39.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做王吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过你的战绩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.92,0:17:46.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救了不少的村落  给予他们独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.76,0:17:49.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也给阿拉尼亚狠打的战斗英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲我是英雄  真不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是斯林，蕾里他们的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.67,0:17:59.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们却把你当成英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.27,0:18:02.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是在这战乱中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以当阿拉尼亚的王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉尼亚也这样盼望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想我胜任不了这个王位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.55,0:18:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做王就像是一个国家的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且那里都是你所救的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以讲出你的条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.93,0:18:27.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在巴里斯很受重视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.93,0:18:30.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在阿拉尼亚时听讲过，是谁传的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你，你别吓一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴里斯国王就是你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依豆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依豆…那个依豆吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.04,0:18:44.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对!他都能当  你怎么当不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.51,0:18:47.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是男人都会梦想当国王的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个最好的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我考虑一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，你慢慢的考虑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案在战争过後告诉我也不迟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你愿意夫雷会全力支持你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.93,0:19:02.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果你能当上王的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.40,0:19:09.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以以更平等的方式相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.24,0:19:13.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我最想要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.09,0:19:23.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打败魔龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁亚喜拉麻莫的野望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.22,0:19:30.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了这罗德岛的未来
